Package com.gadgetbadget.user.security

Class JWK

java.lang.Object
com.gadgetbadget.user.security.JWK
public class JWK
extends java.lang.Object
The class JWK is distributed among all the services as a part of the authentication process implemented by the USER SERVICE. JWK represents the JSON Web Key and used to save and retrieve JWK data to and from the Local Database in each Web Service. JWK data is configured beforehand manually.
Author:
Ishara_Dissanayake
